      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Dialog: Ball-Joint</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2"><text styleclass="Heading2" translate="true">Ball-Joint</text></para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso"><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">See: </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Mechanism-Ball-Joint" styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">Add Ball-Joint</link><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">. Tutorial 12: Design a Spatial Mechanism</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">We use the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Ball-Joint</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> for spatial mechanisms. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">Most often, </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Ball-Joints</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> join </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Parts</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> that are in different </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Mechanism-Editors</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, such that their </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Mechanism-Planes</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> are perpendicular(</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-family:Tahoma;" translate="true">⊥</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">).</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">A </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Ball-Joint</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> must be added two times. One Ball-Joint at each end of one </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Part</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">Open Ball-Joint </text><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">dialog-box</text></para>
